      "text": "<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">A biopsy from the upper lobe of a patient with suspected fungal infection shows budding yeasts with surrounding clear spaces. Which staining technique is most suitable for visualizing these fungal organisms and their characteristic capsules?</span></span></p>",
