      "text": "<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">A researcher is studying a fungal pathogen under the microscope. Which stain is most likely to demonstrate the fungal cell walls and aid in the diagnosis?</span></span></span></span></p>",
